Package ch.nolix.core.generalSkillAPI

The generalSkillAPI is an API that provides interfaces with methods that have a general purpose and are principally suitable for all objects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Castable
    A Castable can return itself casted into a given type.
    IFluentObject<FO extends IFluentObject<FO>>
    A IFluentObject can return itself casted into its concrete type.
    ISmartObject<SO extends ISmartObject<SO>>
    A ISmartObject provides general methods on itself that are independent from its specific purpose.
    Listable<L extends Listable<L>>
    A Listable can return a List that contains the Listable.
    TypeRequestable
    A TypeRequestable has a type.
